snippet.title: Kelly Clarkson - Behind These Hazel Eyes (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Kelly Clarkson's official music video for 'Behind These Hazel Eyes'. Click to listen to Kelly Clarkson on Spotify: http://smarturl.it/KClarkSpot?IQid=KClarkBTHE

As featured on Greatest Hits - Chapter 1. Click to buy the track or album via iTunes: http://smarturl.it/KClarkGHiTunes?IQid=KClarkBTHE
Google Play: http://smarturl.it/KClarkBTHEplay?IQid=KClarkBTHE
Amazon: http://smarturl.it/KClarkGHAmz?IQid=KClarkBTHE

More from Kelly Clarkson
Since U Been Gone: https://youtu.be/R7UrFYvl5TE
Stronger (What Doesn't Kill You): https://youtu.be/Xn676-fLq7I
Breakaway: https://youtu.be/c-3vPxKdj6o

More great 00s videos here: http://smarturl.it/Ultimate00?IQid=KClarkBTHE

Follow Kelly Clarkson
Website: http://www.kellyclarkson.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kellyclarkson
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/kelly_clarkson
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/kellyclarkson

Subscribe to Kelly Clarkson on YouTube: http://smarturl.it/KClarkSub?IQid=KClarkBTHE

---------

Lyrics:

Seems like just yesterday
You were a part of me
I used to stand so tall
I used to be so strong
Your arms around me tight
Everything, it felt so right
Unbreakable, like nothin' could go wrong
Now I can't breathe
No, I can't sleep
I'm barely hanging on

Here I am, once again
I'm torn into pieces
Can't deny it, can't pretend
Just thought you were the one
Broken up, deep inside
But you won't get to see the tears I cry
Behind these hazel eyes
